Anima is a MMORPG Framework\game server for social networks based mostly on C++. It is completely 
open source. If you wish to contribute ideas or code please mail me 
(linked below) or make pull requests to our github repo at 
https://github.com/nonametr/anima

For further information on the Anima project, please visit https://github.com/nonametr/anima

Documentation including installation instructions can be found inside
the doc directory. 